<p>Even the midst of the madness, there is humor. And I like the idea of him using magic to fight magic or whatever the Key is. Or maybe it wasn't magic? Maybe the fact that he believed it was magic made him sane enough to seal up the Key. Whatever, I love this thing.</p>

							</div>

								
